images.prompt: A haunting digital masterpiece depicting a celestial guardian with radiant, feathered wings amidst a surreal, retro pop landscape, illuminated by an eerie twilight radiance that casts ghost gray shadows and neon leaf glows, as fiery petals swirl and incinerate through a tunnel-vision perspective, their smoky tendrils twisting around the luminous figure, whose divine form is both ethereal and imposing, rendered with hyper-realistic textures and vivid color contrasts that evoke a sense of otherworldly serenity intertwined with foreboding mystery, creating an immersive scene where divine power and haunting ambiguity converge in a captivating blend of CGI intricacy and artistic stylization.
